data.description: Motivated Seller! Bring all offers!! Introducing a charming two-bedroom, one-bathroom home with a bonus room, perfect for a nursery or office. The spacious garage is currently being cooled with its own window unit and used as a second living area. The options are endless with this one. The location is perfectly situated in close proximity to the bay and Tyndall Air Force Base. This delightful residence offers a wonderful opportunity for comfortable living in the beautiful Panama City area. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a welcoming living space, featuring ample natural light and a cozy atmosphere. You will find an open kitchen with eat in dining, updated cabinets and ample countertop space. The three bedrooms are generously sized and offer plenty of room and the adjoining door can you give the kids their needed space while added privacy. The bathrooms has fresh white tile shower and new flooring. The home has a large and completely fenced in backyard with room for kids activities, lounge areas or a pool! In summary, this three-bedroom, one-bathroom home presents an incredible opportunity to own a comfortable and affordable property near the bay and Tyndall Air Force Base. With its inviting living spaces, updated features, and convenient location, it promises a lifestyle filled with both tranquility and convenience.
